and they had a gap,

01:26:07.709 --> 01:26:10.081
so, it's like they
asked us to do it.

01:26:10.082 --> 01:26:12.710
So, we say, "Yeah,
we'd love to do it."

01:26:12.711 --> 01:26:14.837
So, we were the first
band to go on.

